Interface Summary

IDocumentCollection Represents a collection of IDocument

IDocumentObjectCollection Represents base interface for entities collections.

ISection Represents a section inside a Document.

IStyleHolder Interface publishes base functionality for style holders
ITable Represents a table in a document.
ITableCollection Represents a collection of ITable.
